content: Finally got Xander's market predictions integrated with real-time data feeds. It's now ready for that investor demo. Also, had a fun day exploring new tech gadgets at a local expo, which gave me some ideas for Xander's hardware setup.

Xander's now got a better understanding of my daily routines and is offering more personalized assistance. Took a break to visit the Brooklyn Museum, which inspired some new visual concepts for Xander's avatar.
